imdb.plot outline: Nathan likes robots. A lot. Like an abnormal amount. Cooped up in his mom's basement, he spends his days fixating on their automaton abilities and dreams of the day that someday he can become one with artificial life. And that's where Chad comes in. Chad is the super computer that Nathan hopes will someday replace his brain. Named after the coolest kid in his elementary school who had quite the luck with the ladies, it's Nathan's hope that by merging man with robot, someday he too can be quite the chick-getter.
